{
  "text": "Tissue was processed as described previously [CITATION_1] ). The following primary antibodies were used: GFP (Abcam, chicken, 1:1000, ab13970/Rockland, goat, 1:500, 600-101-215), Ctip2 (Abcam, rat, 1:250, ab18465), Tbr2 (Abcam, rabbit, 1:150, ab23345), Pax6 (Millipore, rabbit, 1:300, AB2237), Satb2 (self-generated, rabbit, 1:1000), Brn2 (Santa-Cruz, goat, 1:200, sc-6029), Sox5 (Santa-Cruz, goat, sc-17329) and Tbr1 (Abcam, rabbit, 1:200, ab31940) . Dylight/Alexa-coupled secondary antibodies (Jackson ImmunoResearch) were used at 1:500. Hoechst (Sigma, 1:500) or Draq5 (eBioscience, 1:1000) were used for counterstaining.",
  "correct_citation": {
